reviews.text: Delicious food. We came here for lunch. We ordered basil pork and green curry.  The food was delicious and the service was great.  They don't have Thai milk tea which was sad to hear, but we ordered Chang's instead. All for 150 HK$.  I definitely recommend 😁

Awesome Thai food! The food is so flavourful. Highly recommend the crispy pork, fried squid, green curry and minced beef with lettuce wraps. This is my favourite and my go-to Thai place in HK. Cheap beer and good service tops it off!
Okay Thai food for a pretty high price considering the surrounding areas. Okay portion sizes. A bit slow service. Decent amount of seating. English menu. Staff understands English as well. Cash only.
A good place to get thai food while in hong kong
Below average Thai food. Songtham no dried shrimp and not enough lemon. Steam Fish too sweet and fried mince pork too salty.
